{"tid":1796321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「過來人」 未賭過錢既，千奇唔好學賭錢","createTime":"2019-12-24T13:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T14:06:46.000Z","uid":123335,"like":124,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"e032a4b41bc9edbb5f333d1621d4cd879fc30cda","tid":1796321,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"因為學賭錢，背後既代價好大 <br />\n不論係賭場，賭波，賭馬，賭牛熊，期指都一樣 <br />\n<br />\n其一，你將會損失大量金錢作為學費 <br />\n輕則幾萬蚊走唔甩 <br />\n重則十幾廿萬，甚至搞到負債爭街數<br />\n<br />\n其二，你將會損失大量時間 <br />\n學賭錢所消耗既時間，比學投資甚至需要更多 <br />\n炒期炒動物你要識睇倉位、數倉，大戶期結轉倉，好講盤感 <br />\n賭波你要好熟你買果隊波既近況、球員出陣、睇初盤尾盤<br />\n賭馬要睇跑道形勢、睇廠房部署、睇騎師即日狀態、馬匹跟態、檔位、負磅、快地慢地、同程標準時間紀錄 ...etc <br />\n絕對唔好以為學賭錢係一樣簡單既事 <br />\n而你學賭錢既機會成本，係包括職業進修，考牌，讀書，多D時間陪屋企人 .... etc <br />\n<br />\n如果我有得揀多次 <br />\n我會花多D時間進修考牌，搏快D 升職加人工仲實際<br />\n<br />\n我唔想你地行我條舊路"},{"pid":"8ad41eec06841c6b1ec7224c6587afbf2cb4b3b9","tid":1796321,"uid":73241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"bill gor拯救波台眾生<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7ea2759fd80bc6b3f43e58b02bf3f4f750c58a","tid":1796321,"uid":78819,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3etp9u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3etp9u.png&h=20477d2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd9c557fd26e75e8950927e73df8ef8ca5463f1","tid":1796321,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad41eec06841c6b1ec7224c6587afbf2cb4b3b9","tid":1796321,"uid":73241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"bill gor拯救波台眾生<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji